title: Love Letter to Deanoru (Reupload)
author: Five by Five Takes
comment: I’ve watched every single video after watching your video on She-Ra and hope and your narration and editing with the music is chef’s kiss perfection.
As someone who met the original artist and co-creator of this series, Mr. Alphona, I'm quite pleased this show has good fans. To anyone who hasn't read this book, it is spectacular as it sounds.
Love Letter to "The Half of It" directed by Alice Wu :)
Once again, outstanding! Your freezeframe on Nico when she finally understood Karolina's words hurt in the best way, and was something I never picked up on within my several re-watches of the series
O quentinho no coração que esse vídeo oferece ❤️
